pageProduct.name: Thompson's One-A-Day Tribulus 20000mg 120 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's One-A-Day Tribulus 20000 Traditionally used in Ayurvedic medicine to improve healthy libido and as body tonic.

Thompson's One-A-Day Tribulus contains Tribulus which has traditionally been used in Ayurvedic medicine (traditional Indian medicine) to improve healthy libido and as body tonic.

Size: 120caps

Oil-Free?: Yes

KEY FEATURES

• Traditionally been used in Ayurvedic Medicine (traditional Indian medicine) as a tonic and aphrodisiac.
• Vegetarian/Vegan friendly.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional.

CAUTION

Keep out of reach of children.
Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains:
Tribulus terrestris (Tribulus) ext. 400mg
derived from dry fruit 20g (20000mg)

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
